## Scope of this licence

This licence applies to the design assets distributed in this folder:

- `emblem-16.svg`, `emblem-32.svg`, `emblem-64.svg`
- `wordmark-full.svg`, `wordmark-silent.svg`
- `tokens.css`

These files are distributed copies from the upstream `threehouse-plus-ec/cd-rules`
repository under Model B propagation (CD 0.10). The upstream declaration of
MIT for these specific files appears in `blueprint-threehouse-CD.md` Section
0.3 ("Licence matrix", row "Design assets") and Section "Asset registry"
(table naming each file as MIT). Provenance, commit SHA, and per-file SHA-256
checksums are recorded in `SOURCE.md`.

The MIT grant here is a downstream restatement of the upstream-declared
licence for convenience and clarity at the folder boundary; the authoritative
licence declaration remains the cd-rules blueprint.

